<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Placement Drive Invitation</title>
<style>
body {
font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
line-height: 1.6;
}

.container {
max-width: 600px;
margin: 0 auto;
padding: 20px;
border: 1px solid #ccc;
}

.header {
text-align: center;
margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.details {
background-color: #f9f9f9;
padding: 10px;
border: 1px solid #ccc;
}

.details h3 {
margin: 0;
padding-bottom: 5px;
border-bottom: 1px solid #ccc;
}

.details p {
margin: 0;
}

.cta-button {
text-align: center;
margin-top: 20px;
}

.cta-button a {
display: inline-block;
background-color: #007bff;
color: #fff;
text-decoration: none;
padding: 10px 20px;
border-radius: 5px;
}

.footer {
text-align: center;
margin-top: 20px;
color: #888;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Placement Drive Invitation</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="details">
            <h3>Event Details:</h3>
            <p><strong>Date:</strong> ${EventDate}</p>
            <p><strong>Time:</strong> ${EventTime}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-button">
            <a href="/">Click here to Register</a>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you have any questions or need further information, please reply to this email or contact us at [Your Contact Email] or call [Your Contact Phone Number].</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
